omy/global-economy/article/3256119/china-ev-exports-slammed-wests-trade-barriers-find-greener-pastures-free-trade-partners?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>一月和二月的海关数据显示，反补贴调查和贸易限制正在对新能源行业造成影响，使电动汽车生产商面临被挤出市场的风险。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 16:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3256119/china-ev-exports-slammed-wests-trade-barriers-find-greener-pastures-free-trade-partners?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>英特尔从华盛顿获得 195 亿美元用于建设和改善芯片工厂</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3256140/intel-gets-us195-billion-washington-build-and-improve-chip-factories?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>美国商务部的赠款和贷款是 2022 年《芯片与科学法案》的一部分，旨在加强供应链并对抗中国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 15:45:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3256140/intel-gets-us195-billion-washington-build-and-improve-chip-factories?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>苹果首席执行官蒂姆·库克在中国这个全球最大智能手机市场的 iPhone 销量疲软之际发起魅力攻势</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3256130/apple-ceo-tim-cook-goes-charm-offensive-china-amid-weak-iphone-sales-worlds-largest-smartphone?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>周三，在繁忙的上海行程中，库克会见了中国视频游戏开发商、电影制片人和比亚迪的亿万富翁创始人。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 14:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3256130/apple-ceo-tim-cook-goes-charm-offensive-china-amid-weak-iphone-sales-worlds-largest-smartphone?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国加大力度寻找外国投资和高科技公司，但北京会采取行动吗？</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3256114/china-ups-ante-hunt-foreign-investment-hi-tech-firms-will-beijing-follow-through-actions?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>国家主席习近平本周早些时候视察了一家中德合资锂电池材料公司，随后国务院还公布了针对外国投资者和侨民的措施。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 13:30:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3256114/china-ups-ante-hunt-foreign-investment-hi-tech-firms-will-beijing-follow-through-actions?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>北京就马尼拉“最近与中国有关的负面言论”向菲律宾大使提出抗议</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3256082/beijing-protests-philippine-ambassador-over-recent-negative-china-related-remarks-manila?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>同一天，中国驻菲律宾大使馆表示，华盛顿不应在南海“挑起事端”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 13:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3256082/beijing-protests-philippine-ambassador-over-recent-negative-china-related-remarks-manila?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>在该地区最近发生几起事件后，台湾将在金门和其他岛屿举行海上实弹军事演习</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3256123/taiwan-stage-offshore-live-fire-military-drills-after-several-recent-incidents-same-area?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>炮兵演习定于四月份在台湾近海岛屿举行，其中包括金门岛，上个月，金门岛有两名渔民在海岸警卫队的追击中丧生。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 12:31:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3256123/taiwan-stage-offshore-live-fire-military-drills-after-several-recent-incidents-same-area?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国贵州官员在启动调查逮捕女商人数周后面临腐败调查</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3256110/officials-chinas-guizhou-face-corruption-investigation-weeks-after-launch-probe-arrest-businesswoman?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>这两名官员与国有度假村有联系，据称该度假村欠建筑公司老板数百万美元，后者在拒绝和解提议后因“寻衅滋事”而被捕。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 11:00:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3256110/officials-chinas-guizhou-face-corruption-investigation-weeks-after-launch-probe-arrest-businesswoman?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国总理李强将访问澳大利亚，堪培拉继续推动取消贸易壁垒</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3256089/chinese-premier-li-qiang-visit-australia-canberra-continues-push-lift-trade-barriers?